content.rendered:
Directed by Abhishek Chaubey.

Written by Abhishek Chaubey. Sudip Sharma.

Cast Shahid Kapoor(Tommy Singh). Alia Bhatt(Kumari Pinky). Kareena Kapoor(Preet Sahani). Diljit Dosanjh(Sartaj Singh). Satish Kaushik(Tayaji). Manav Vij(Jujhar Singh).Vansh Bhardwaj. Suhail Nayyar(Jassi). Prabhjyot Singh(Balli). Rajesh Kumar Sharma(Kaka). Kamal Tiwari(M.P. Maninder Brar (as Kamal Tewari)). Mahabir Bhullar(Veerji). Suvinder Vicky(Kukku). Dilawar Sidhu(Bhandi). Lovely Sidhu(Vesper Rider 1). Vishu Sharma(Vesper Rider 2). Harpreet Singh(Shamsher). Gurpreet Toti(Constable 1). Ikhattar Singh(Constable 2). Pargat Singh(Constable 3). Gaurav Sharma(Constable 4). Zeeshan Balouch(Smuggler). Geetangali Singh(Gursimran). Amar Chaudhary(Shyam). Sukh Kunwar(Birmingham Boys 1 (as Sukh)). Harrdy Sandhu(Birmingham Boys 2 (as Hardy)). Annastasia Hamulka(Emo chick (as Anastasiya Hamolka)). Kaizaad Kotwal(Speedy boy 1 (as Kaizad Kotwal)). Vishal Handa(Speedy boy 2). Pawan Singh(Truck driver). Ishaan Khattar(Boy at party). Aaradhna Uppal(News anchor (as Aradhana Uppal)). Satwant Kaur(Sartaj’s mom). Anita Shabdeesh(Sartaj’s aunt). Satpal Singh(Sartaj’s chacha). Nina Tiwana(Beeji). Swairaj Sandhu(Pahalwan). Ravi Aneja(Pehalwan gang member 1). Sandeep Jit Pateela(Pehalwan gang member 2).

Languages Hindi. Punjabi. Bhojpuri.

Producers Sankalp Acharekar. Vivek b Agrawal. Vikas Bahl. Sada Bhuvad. Dilip Borkar. Tanvi Gandhi. Aman Gill. Gurpreet Gill. Ekta Kapoor. Shobha Kapoor. Anurag Kashyap. Madhu Mantena Varma. Vikramaditya Motwane. Sameer Nair. Lalit Paikray. Gabbar Sangrur. Karishma Naina Sharma.

Production Phantom Films.
